ji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cfe7000b990776f9e24c05463f4314a9540131","tid":332474,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>捱夜通常都係玩電話 / 打機</blockquote><br />\n要還就真既... 過咗廿歲已經明白</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n係，健康係唔會一下出現問題，通常積累一段時間就大爆發，識個人，因為捱夜搞到腎衰竭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143efb7ec4a2cc6623ebfcb7236ff8dd0abec8c3","tid":332474,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主捱到有乜病徵？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n病就冇，但感覺到打工起碼做10年以上，<br />\n如果經常捱夜做野，心諗30歲個身體仲頂唔頂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6a9b89502541c1df75137f16ccd5ceb2dd56c9","tid":332474,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:50:02.000Z","msg":"經常鳩hea到2點先訓<br />\n7點鐘又起身返工<br />\n會唔會短幾年命"},{"pid":"b5e25771a2c1457449fe1c456132ea6c5b3611b5","tid":332474,"uid":119272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經常鳩hea到2點先訓<br />\n7點鐘又起身返工<br />\n會唔會短幾年命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好肯定，會"},{"pid":"532e5fce02500ffc0d9b53a9f0709a967ca7cb55","tid":332474,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經常鳩hea到2點先訓<br />\n7點鐘又起身返工<br />\n會唔會短幾年命</blockquote><br />\n應該無abc更咁衰掛"},{"pid":"00e32a449345cc902b108443ae04cf96d40dfee3","tid":332474,"uid":61418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"幾年晚晚兩點先訓 好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c505ed74ba48bcb1e9d978db475e483ed074ccc8","tid":332474,"uid":49944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T22:29:00.000Z","msg":"係，現家已經體會到<br />\n當時冇得簡，頂硬上，結果，身體真係差左好多。"},{"pid":"0bcccf77d1e19702dc62d7542372c4f3beec87d8","tid":332474,"uid":74428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r